i just spent $60 in the last few (possibly couple) days. in exchange for all that money, i now claim possession to:
  1. a blue drawstring bag
  2. a striped cami
  3. a violet cami
  4. a pair of denim shorts
  5. a pair of terry capris for my sister
  6. a lime green bra
  7. a bottle of sunscreen plus mini keychain bottle
  8. a overly small flute tee
  9. a white esprit tee
  10. a pair of bleached capris
so if i really need to justify all that spending, each item only costed $6. that's actually not too bad.

my job is so fucked up. things happen in a week, then i find out about it two weeks later. work gets backed up in other departments, and when the listings eventually do come to me, they've already closed. then they move the server without telling me, in the process deleting a major portion of my image archives, thereby making the site useless. seriously, i need to spend a week on php and fix this major disconnection between everything and everything i need to do thrice. but i also need to be able to drive in a week. speaking of which i'll be able to drive in a week provided i pass my road test i'm so not ready.

livejournal is very odd. looking over my previous entries, i've noticed that one was from january, one march, and now july. i'll never understand why when i put in pink, it comes out olive. EDIT { apparently clicking the "submit" button does help the process. who woulda thought... } END EDIT hm...
